import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { UserService } from '../user.service'; import { IUser } from 'src/models'; @Component({ selector: 'app-admission', templateUrl: './admission.component.html', styleUrls: ['./admission.component.css'] }) export class AdmissionComponent { users: IUser[]; constructor(private userService: UserService) {} ngOnInit() { this.userService.getUsers().subscribe((users) => { this.users = users; }); } }
